    <dl>
        <dt><dfn>P1</dfn></dt>
        <dd>Let all communications be limited to light speed</dd>
        </dl>
    <dl>
        <dt><dfn>P2</dfn></dt>
        <dd>Let morality be an aspect of rational being that values reason above all</dd>
